---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Distribution Round #1 — Open Source Endowment" description="OSE's first distribution round: $12,000 of endowment returns funding critical open source projects through our open, community-developed model.">
    <article>
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="pagesec pagesec--dark pagesec--tight">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="insec insec--xpad insec--ytight">
                    <div class="squares squares--corner-dark-sw-outer"></div>
                    <div class="squares squares--corner-dark-sw-inner"></div>
                    <div class="squares squares--corner-dark-ne-outer"></div>
                    <div class="squares squares--corner-dark-ne-inner"></div>
                    <div class="distribution-intro">
                        <div class="sechead sechead--min-height sechead--left">
                            <h1>Distribution Round #1</h1>
                            <p class="round-type">Proactive</p>
                            <p>
                                OSE's inaugural distribution round, funded by returns earned
                                on the endowment during our incorporating year. Awarded projects
                                will be selected through the first implementation of our open,
                                community-developed model.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="distribution-kpi">
                            <b>$12,000</b>
                            <span>to be distributed to critical, underfunded open source projects</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About This Round + Selection Process -->
        <section class="pagesec">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="insec insec--xpad">
                    <div class="about-and-process">
                        <div class="round-details">
                            <h2 class="sechead sechead--left">About This Round</h2>
                            <p>
                                This round proactively identifies critical open source infrastructure that is
                                under-resourced relative to its importance. Projects do not apply.
                                We find them and reach out directly.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Funds are intended to help projects become more secure and stable,
                                whether that means addressing maintainer burnout, closing security gaps,
                                or de-risking software the world depends on. Individual distributions are
                                expected to be under $5,000 per project.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Projects are selected through our open
                                <a href="https://github.com/osendowment/model" target="_blank">model</a>,
                                co-developed with the community and voted on by
                                <a href="/endowment">Members</a> (donors of $1,000+).
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Awarded projects will be determined and contacted by <strong>May 31</strong>.
                            </p>
                            <div class="eligibility-note">
                                <h3>Eligibility</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Only independent free and open source software is eligible — no corporate-backed projects,
                                    no projects with associated startups. See our <a href="/faq">FAQ</a> to learn more about eligibility.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="selection-process">
                            <h3 class="process-heading">Selection Process</h3>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <div><strong>Model Development</strong><p>Community and Members contribute to model design</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <div><strong>Member Vote</strong><p>Members select which model to use for this round</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>3</span>
                                <div><strong>Model Runs</strong><p>Algorithm evaluates projects and generates rankings</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>4</span>
                                <div><strong>Human Review</strong><p>Staff and community review outputs for accuracy</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>5</span>
                                <div><strong>Project Selection</strong><p>Final projects chosen based on review</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>6</span>
                                <div><strong>Project Outreach</strong><p>Projects contacted to confirm eligibility and interest</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>7</span>
                                <div><strong>Due Diligence</strong><p>Legal and logistical review of selected projects</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <span>8</span>
                                <div><strong>Board Approval</strong><p>Board reviews and approves final distribution</p></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Nomination Form -->
        <section class="pagesec">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="insec insec--xpad">
                    <div class="nomination-section">
                        <h2 class="sechead sechead--left">Nominate a Project</h2>
                        <p class="nomination-intro">
                            Know a critical open source project that deserves support?
                            Help us identify projects our model might not yet surface. Nominations will be considered in the model for this round.
                        </p>
                        <iframe
                            src="https://app.formbricks.com/s/cmkn0e39m3nkcad01mrxfudbp"
                            title="Nominate a Project"
                            frameborder="0"
                            class="nomination-embed"
                        ></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Hero */
    .sechead h1 {
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .round-type {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: var(--font-size-3);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }
    .distribution-intro {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 4rem;
        @media (max-width: 800px) {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
        .distribution-kpi {
            margin-top: 5.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            @media (max-width: 800px) {
                margin-top: 0;
            }
            b {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 1.0rem;
                font-size: var(--font-size-8);
                font-weight: normal;
                line-height: 1;
                @media (max-width: 800px) {
                    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                    font-size: var(--font-size-6);
                }
            }
        }
    }

    /* About This Round + Process layout */
    .about-and-process {
        display: flex;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 3rem;
        }
    }
    .round-details {
        flex: 2;
        h2.sechead {
            padding-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
    }
    .eligibility-note {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-section-border);
        border-top: 2px solid var(--color-primary-border);
        h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: var(--font-size-3);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--color-text-dark-secondary);
        }
    }

    /* Selection Process */
    .selection-process {
        flex: 1;
    }
    .process-heading {
        margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
        font-size: var(--font-size-2);
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    /* Nomination Form */
    .nomination-intro {
        max-width: 36rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: var(--font-size-3);
        color: var(--color-text-dark-secondary);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .process-step {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        padding: 0.35rem 0;
        span {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 1.4rem;
            height: 1.4rem;
            margin-top: 0.1rem;
            background: var(--color-gray);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-section-border);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: var(--font-size-2);
        }
        strong {
            font-size: var(--font-size-2);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: var(--font-size-1);
            opacity: 0.55;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
    }

    /* Nomination Form Embed */
    .nomination-embed {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 500px;
        border: none;
    }
</style>
